.SH NAME
dotty-git - Git helpers built on dotty's commit signing.


.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBdotty git  [flags]\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
Helpers that drive git through dotty's hardware-backed signing. Set signing
up first with \fBdotty signing-key sign --print-git-config\fR\&.


.SH OPTIONS
\fB-h\fP, \fB--help\fP[=false]
	help for git


.SH OPTIONS INHERITED FROM PARENT COMMANDS
\fB--profile\fP=""
	profile to operate on (defaults to the active profile)


.SH EXAMPLE
.EX
  dotty git resign HEAD~3
  dotty git resign --root --reset-author
.EE


.SH SEE ALSO
\fBdotty(1)\fP, \fBdotty-git-resign(1)\fP
